{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_018T1uZ9bHPbQWjJ53Cdxwxz","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete picture of the application. Let me analyze the migration requirements:\n\n**Current state:** This is a Spring Boot + JoinFaces (JSF) application that:\n- Uses Spring Boot for dependency injection, JPA, and web serving\n- Uses JSF (Jakarta Faces) via JoinFaces for the UI layer\n- Already uses `jakarta.*` namespace for persistence, validation, and faces\n- Uses Spring annotations (`@Configuration`, `@Service`, `@Repository`, `@Component`, `@Autowired`, `@Scope`, `@Transactional`)\n\n**Target:** Migrate from Spring to pure Jakarta EE (no Spring dependencies). This means:\n- Replace Spring Boot with a Jakarta EE runtime (e.g., Open Liberty, WildFly, Payara)\n- Replace Spring DI with CDI (Jakarta Contexts and Dependency Injection)\n- Replace Spring Data JPA with JPA EntityManager\n- Replace Spring `@Transactional` with Jakarta `@Transactional`\n- Remove JoinFaces (not needed - pure Jakarta EE provides JSF natively)"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":695,"cache_read_input_tokens":41701,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":695,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":811},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d9614706-aa1e-4ee0-a2cc-4f8232e667d9","uuid":"18264bfe-8d18-4e69-a8d7-fecfb1033465"}
