{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01WRjtsWsXtEtgHuxHxBfqYa","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me rewrite all Java files. The package will change from `com.example.addressbookspring` to `com.example.addressbook` to reflect the removal of Spring. I'll also need to restructure:\n\n1. Remove `Application.java` (Spring Boot main class) - not needed in Jakarta EE\n2. Remove `ServletInitializer.java` - not needed\n3. Remove `SpringConfig.java` - not needed (CDI scans automatically with beans.xml)\n4. Remove `JsfConfig.java` - not needed (JSF is configured via web.xml/faces-config.xml in Jakarta EE)\n5. Remove `ContactRepository.java` (Spring Data) - replace with EntityManager in service\n6. Rewrite `ContactService.java` - use `@PersistenceContext EntityManager` and `@Transactional`\n7. Rewrite `ContactController.java` - use CDI `@Named`, `@SessionScoped`, `@Inject`\n\nLet me do all the file operations:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":603,"cache_read_input_tokens":47754,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":603,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":428},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d9614706-aa1e-4ee0-a2cc-4f8232e667d9","uuid":"e98876ca-4019-4ea8-8222-400f816bbce4"}
